  their sleep questionnaire application, feeling it was too generic and lacked
  visual appeal. The assistant conducted a comprehensive review of the app's
  styling, including global CSS, layout, and individual components. Based on
  this analysis, the assistant identified several areas for improvement, such as
  the color palette, typography, spacing, form elements, and overall visual
  interest. The approach taken was to transform the visual language to evoke a
  sense of calm and professionalism, specifically tailored for a sleep
  assessment experience. This involved implementing a new sleep-themed color
  palette with deeper indigo/purple tones and soft teal accents, refining the
   layout, enhancing the progress bar, and redesigning the
   with better visual hierarchy and engaging feature cards. The
  outcome is a more polished and inviting user interface that aligns with the
  app's purpose.
